---
import Header from "../Components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../Components/Footer.astro";
import "../styles/global.css";
---



<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <title>FAQs</title>
  </head>
    <Header />
    <section class="w-full bg-black text-white py-16 px-4">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-10" style="color: var(--gold)">FAQs</h2>

            <div class="space-y-6">
            <!-- FAQ Item -->
            <details class="border rounded-xl p-4 bg-dark_gray/40" style="border-color: var(--gold)">
                <summary class="cursor-pointer font-semibold text-light_gray flex justify-between items-center">
                Do I have to have a background in running, swimming, and biking?
                </summary>
                <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-white">No, any experience level is welcome!</p>
            </details>

            <details class="border rounded-xl p-4 bg-dark_gray/40" style="border-color: var(--gold)">
                <summary class="cursor-pointer font-semibold text-light_gray flex justify-between items-center">
                Are there tryouts?
                </summary>
                <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-white">Nope! Everyone is welcome to join!</p>
            </details>

            <details class="border rounded-xl p-4 bg-dark_gray/40" style="border-color: var(--gold)">
                <summary class="cursor-pointer font-semibold text-light_gray flex justify-between items-center">
                What if I am not the best swimmer?
                </summary>
                <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-white">Our coaches are amazing teachers and ready to help.</p>
            </details>

            <details class="border rounded-xl p-4 bg-dark_gray/40" style="border-color: var(--gold)">
                <summary class="cursor-pointer font-semibold text-light_gray flex justify-between items-center">
                Can I join if I don't have a bike?
                </summary>
                <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-white">Yes, we have rentals, sponsors, and resources!</p>
            </details>

            <details class="border rounded-xl p-4 bg-dark_gray/40" style="border-color: var(--gold)">
                <summary class="cursor-pointer font-semibold text-light_gray flex justify-between items-center">
                What essentials will I need for the three disciplines?
                </summary>
                <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-white">
                Swim: goggles, cap, swimsuit<br>
                Bike: helmet, bike, flat kit, hydration, and fuel<br>
                Run: running shoes
                </p>
            </details>

            <details class="border rounded-xl p-4 bg-dark_gray/40" style="border-color: var(--gold)">
                <summary class="cursor-pointer font-semibold text-light_gray flex justify-between items-center">
                What does it cost to be on the team?
                </summary>
                <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-white">110 for the semester, 200 for the year.</p>
            </details>

            <details class="border rounded-xl p-4 bg-dark_gray/40" style="border-color: var(--gold)">
                <summary class="cursor-pointer font-semibold text-light_gray flex justify-between items-center">
                What if I can't make it to every practice?
                </summary>
                <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-white">No problem, just make it to what your schedule allows!</p>
            </details>

            <details class="border rounded-xl p-4 bg-dark_gray/40" style="border-color: var(--gold)">
                <summary class="cursor-pointer font-semibold text-light_gray flex justify-between items-center">
                When can I join?
                </summary>
                <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-white">There will be an interest meeting at the beginning of each semester, announced via Instagram. Following that, there will be a period to sign up for the club!</p>
            </details>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>



  <Footer/>
</html>
